Φ(SR) = δγ(encoding|initial-consolidation) ⇄ δγ(forgetting|natural-decay) → [σ(retrieval-attempt|effortful-recall)] → [δγ(spaced-review|reconsolidation)] ⇄ [δγ(expanding-intervals)] → [κ(durable-memory)] + [λ(mastery)] ⊗ [μ(structured-schedule)] | :metabolic-learning

