=== Dimensional Analysis ===

Cycling Field (δγ):
  - The forgetting curve as natural metabolic process
  - Expanding intervals matching memory consolidation
  - Rhythmic review as metabolic cycle
  - Earth-dominant: grounding, returning, deepening
  - The core insight: timing matters more than intensity

Structure Field (μ):
  - Algorithmic optimization of review schedules
  - Systematic organization of knowledge decks
  - Structured progression toward mastery
  - Metal-quality: organizing, systematizing, scheduling

Distinction Field (σ):
  - Effortful retrieval distinguishes known from forgotten
  - Testing effect through active recall
  - Pattern recognition of what needs review
  - Air-quality: clarifying, distinguishing, revealing

Integration Field (κ):
  - Memory reconsolidation at higher baseline
  - Weaving knowledge into long-term storage
  - Cumulative building of durable knowledge
  - Earth-quality: grounding, embedding, stabilizing

Direction Field (λ):
  - Purposeful progression toward mastery
  - Motivation to maintain daily practice
  - The "why" that sustains the discipline
  - Fire-quality: directional, purposeful, driving

